data.title: Murder of Justina Morales
data.meta_description: Justina Morales was an American girl from the Bedford-Stuyvesant section of Brooklyn, New York, who was killed at the age of eight years by her mother's boyfriend, Luis Santiago, on New Year's Eve in 1995. Her body was never found. The killing gained notoriety primarily through the New York City newspapers.
